      <section>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Why We Do This</h2>
        <p>
          There are a lot of great podcasts out there that will claim to teach you everything you need to know about photography and shooting weddings. We are not that podcast.
          Why not? Because we’re the best photography podcast, and we know that education is boring and depressing.
        </p>
        <p>
          And let’s face it, the world is a depressing place sometimes — and running a wedding photography business doesn’t shelter you from the downtimes.
          This podcast exists to help you decompress, and if you need, to laugh the horrors of this unforgiving world away. That got dark.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Leave Behinds</h2>
        <p>
          Other podcasts give you takeaways. Things you can takeaway from the podcast and apply to your business.
          We firmly believe it will be best if you leave behind everything you hear on our podcast.
        </p>
        <p>
          The only takeaways we hope you have at the end of each episode is a smile on your face, a pep in your step, and a flutter in your heart.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <blockquote>
          <p>“…it’s a brilliant mix of incredibly helpful advice and irreverent humor.”</p>
          <cite>— Heidi Thompson, <a href="https://www.evolveyourweddingbusiness.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">evolveyourweddingbusiness.com</a></cite>
        </blockquote>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">About Steve</h2>
        <img src="/images/why/steve-jenn.webp" alt="This is Steve!" class="profile-image" />
