        </p>
        <p>
          In recent years he’s put the paddle down and picked up a camera. He’s a photographer in Noblesville, Indiana, shooting weddings for over 10 years with his wife Jenn under Van Elk & Co.
        </p>
        <p>
          Unlike Dustin, Steve has tripped and fallen and hit his head while shooting weddings — and several times on commercial shoots. He’s missing some brain cells and it’s safe to say he has much to learn from his mentor, Dustin, about head safety.
        </p>
        <p><strong>Likes:</strong> Spicy food, beer, bathroom mirror selfies, and podcasting greatness.</p>
        <p><strong>Dislikes:</strong> Dustin’s bridge-tripping camera.</p>
        <p><strong>Aliases:</strong> Great Indiana Man, 5th Grade Paddle Ball Champ, Sweet Steve, Stevsie, Van Elkostein, Stevie V.</p>
        <p><strong>Links:</strong> <a href="https://vanelk.co" target="_blank">vanelk.co</a>, <a href="https://stevenvanelk.com" target="_blank">stevenvanelk.com</a>, <a href="https://redwoodlane.net" target="_blank">redwoodlane.net</a></p>
