      <section>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">About Dustin</h2>
        <img src="/images/why/dustin-corynn.webp" alt="This is Dustin!" class="profile-image" />
        <p>
          Dustin McKibben couldn’t be bothered to write his own bio, so I (Steve) did it for him. Dustin is a photographer in Fort Wayne, Indiana. No one brings the awesome quite like Dustin.
        </p>
        <p>
          He’s been shooting weddings for over 10 years and has never tripped over a camera. He also does a lot of commercial and real estate work under the name Art Home Photo.
        </p>
        <p>
